:::Obsidian/Bludgeon:::

::Obsidian and Bludgeon receive Kitkats transmission nad go to the hold::
Bludgeon: good to see you again Obsidian.
Obsidian: Yes its been too long.
::Back in the great war Obsidian was a general under Bludgeon's leadership::
Obsidian: How is it that you are alive?
Bludgeon: As you know, i was destroyed by the original Megatron and used as 
parts for his Warworld.  When the quantum surge hit me, i became a Transmetal 
and lost my Pretender shell.  I wandered the universe for ages until i found 
earth.  Now i have joined the Predacons.
::They finish gathering the weapons, pack them up, and take them to KitKat::
Obsidian: We have finished.
